  "active_lock_reason": null,
  "body": "Currently in initial sync we fetch blocks in parallel to processing them. Now that we have BLS verification in threads we could also parallelize signature verification.\r\n\r\nWhile processing block batch N we could verify the signature set of batch N+1. Depending on the time cost of epoch transitions vs sig verification we could increase the sync speed by x2.\r\n\r\nAfter merging https://github.com/ChainSafe/lodestar/pull/2421 we would have metrics to time the sig verification cost",
